1. `bundle package` (caches gems)
1. configure `production.rb` like development
1. `RAILS_ENV=production bundle exec rails db:create` threw errors about encryption. i had to move some old encryption files out of the way so new ones could regenerate
  1. `mv config/credentials.yml.enc config/credentials.yml.enc.old`
  2. `mv config/master.key config/master.key.old`
1. Create and migrate the db: `bx rails db:create RAILS_ENV=production`, then `bx rails db:migrate RAILS_ENV=production`


test this as root:
sudo -u syblius -i /Users/syblius/workspace/log-thyself/scripts/launch.sh
